			"condition": "",
			"prompt": "Before you go, let me tell you what I can do with the light. You can ask me to turn it on or off, make it brighter or dimmer, and make it cooler or warmer. And after you give me a command, you can say things like <pitch mult='1.2'>brighter</pitch>, or <break size='0.12'/> <pitch mult='1.1'>warmer</pitch>, to fine tune the look. If you don't ask for a specific room, I'll use ${defaultRoom} by <phoneme ph='d ii f o l t'>default</phoneme>. <break size='0.3'/>This'll be <pitch mult='1.3'>fun</pitch>!",
